Modules of LankaTutor
---------------------

LankaTutor contains two main subsystems. Those are resource platforms, and the other one is the learning platform. You can either use one of the subsystems for the registration/sign up process. After the successful registration, you can log in to our website and use those two resources simultaneously because the two subsystems interconnected with each other.

